Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In 2049, World War III broke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The flames of nuclear war devoured the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and humans’ future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A fatal plague, caused be a mutating virus, 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is rapidly spreading over the post-apocalyptic world. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The world needs your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, play the role of a governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and take your duty to save the city and the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with limited resources and new technologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called “Age of Plague”.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In each level, the player initially has 10 cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's allowed to replace at most 3 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,, Each level corresponds to a city and contains cards peculiar to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, we are now in St. Petersburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the high latitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the resources that can be harvested from land are very limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, people created a weather control system
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to adapt to the environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,which is represented by Blizzard and Drought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The virus in the game spreads in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,similar to that in Conway's game of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The player can view information of the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As the player proceeds to next levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he gets more resources which allows him to draw and use more cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Danyu Zhou: Project 2 is no doubt hard and time consuming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Without having effective teamwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be a lot harder for us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to create something equivalent to what we have accomplished now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jigang Li: In P2, I gained lots of experience in flat design. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,, I gradually learned how to employ an adaptive workflow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,not only as an individual, but also as a member of our team. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Haifeng Jia: Web designing is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, I will definitely study more knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,about front-end development.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zefang Wei: Teamwork must be the most critical experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in developing our project 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite difficulties and challenges,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy our game!
